## Overview
QUICKAI is a comprehensive AI SaaS platform built to streamline creative and professional workflows. The application provides:
- AI Image Generation and Creative Editing
- Intelligent Text Content Creation
- Automated Resume Review and Optimization
- Precise Background and Object Removal
- Catchy Article and Blog Title Generation
- Community Sharing Features

The platform is built using the robust PERN stack (PostgreSQL, Express, React, Node.js) and integrates seamlessly with OpenAI's advanced intelligence models.

---

## Key Features

### AI-Powered Tools
- Generate Images: Instantly create high-quality visuals from text prompts.
- Remove Background: Automatic, precise background isolation for uploaded images.
- Remove Objects: Effortlessly clean up images by erasing unwanted objects.
- Write Articles: Smart, AI-assisted full-length article generation.
- Blog Titles: Generate highly engaging, SEO-friendly blog post headlines.
- Review Resume: Advanced AI resume analysis, scoring, and targeted suggestions.

### User Experience
- Secure Authentication: Production-ready user management powered by Clerk.
- Central Dashboard: A unified, user-friendly hub to access all AI services.
- Community Hub: Public feed to share your AI creations and discover community work.
- Fully Responsive Design: Optimized layout for seamless use across mobile, tablet, and desktop screens.
- Real-time Processing: Fast streaming and processing for instant AI feedback.

### Enterprise Architecture
- Secure File Handling: Reliable media management via Cloudinary integration.
- Document Processing: Instant PDF parsing for structural resume analysis.
- Scalable Backbone: Asynchronous handling designed to support high-traffic loads.
- API-First Methodology: Designed around structured, predictable RESTful endpoints.

---

## Tech Stack

### Frontend Client
- React - Component-based user interface framework
- Vite - High-performance frontend build tool
- Tailwind CSS - Utility-first styling framework
- Axios - Promise-based HTTP client for seamless API communications
- React Router DOM - Declarative routing for single-page applications
- Lucide React - Modern, clean icon library
- React Hot Toast - Sleek, responsive UI notifications
- React Markdown - Secure rendering for AI-generated markdown text
- Clerk React - Streamlined client-side authentication

### Backend Server
- Node.js - Scalable JavaScript runtime environment
- Express - Fast, minimalist web framework for routing and middleware
- PostgreSQL - Robust relational database layer hosted on Neon
- OpenAI Node SDK - Deep integration with text and image generation models
- Cloudinary SDK - Automated cloud media optimization and storage
- Multer - Node.js middleware for handling multipart form data and file uploads
- CORS - Configured cross-origin resource sharing controls
- PDF-Parse - Structural text extraction from uploaded PDF documents

### DevOps and Infrastructure
- Vercel - Optimized frontend hosting and deployment
- Neon - Serverless, scalable PostgreSQL database hosting
- Cloudinary CDN - Global asset and image delivery network
- Clerk Dashboard - Cloud-hosted user session management

